---
title: Creamy Truffle and Tenderstem® Linguine with Rosemary and Hazelnuts
description: Our Creamy Truffle and Tenderstem® Linguine is a delicious veggie option that makes it easy to eat more veg in your diet and try something new!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R21_W51_UK_V18106-2_Main__2low-a41fbb8e.jpg
